---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Restaurant Review Layout Preview" description="Design preview of the restaurant review article template.">

  <!-- Launch Banner -->
  <div class="launch-banner">
    We're launching soon — this is a design preview
  </div>

  <!-- ===== ARTICLE HEADER ===== -->
  <header class="article-header">
    <div class="article-pillar-tag"><a href="/thehansang/eat/">Eat</a> &middot; Review</div>
    <h1>Restaurant Review Layout Preview</h1>
    <div class="article-byline">
      <span class="author">Author Name</span>
      <span class="separator">/</span>
      <time>Coming Soon</time>
      <span class="separator">/</span>
      <span>8 min read</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- ===== FEATURED IMAGE ===== -->
  <figure class="article-featured-image">
    <div class="image-placeholder">[ Featured Image Placeholder ]</div>
    <figcaption>Photo caption placeholder. Credit: The Hansang</figcaption>
  </figure>

  <!-- Video embed placeholder -->
  <div class="article-video">
    <div class="article-video-inner">
      <div class="article-video-placeholder">
        <div class="article-video-play"></div>
        <span>Watch on Instagram</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="article-video-caption">Video embed placeholder</p>
  </div>

  <!-- ===== ARTICLE LAYOUT ===== -->
  <div class="article-layout">

    <!-- MAIN CONTENT -->
    <article class="article-content">

      <!-- Quick Take -->
      <aside class="quick-take" aria-label="Quick summary">
        <div class="quick-take-title">Quick Take</div>
        <div class="quick-take-grid">
          <div class="quick-take-item">
            <span class="quick-take-label">Rating</span>
            <span class="quick-take-value rating">X.X / 10</span>
          </div>
          <div class="quick-take-item">
            <span class="quick-take-label">Price Range</span>
            <span class="quick-take-value">$$&ndash;$$$</span>
          </div>
          <div class="quick-take-item">
            <span class="quick-take-label">Best Dish</span>
            <span class="quick-take-value">Dish Name Placeholder</span>
          </div>
          <div class="quick-take-item">
            <span class="quick-take-label">Skip This</span>
            <span class="quick-take-value">Dish Name Placeholder</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </aside>

      <p>This is a design preview of the restaurant review article layout. The text you are reading is placeholder content that demonstrates the typographic hierarchy, spacing, and overall reading experience of The Hansang review template.</p>

      <p>Each review will follow a consistent structure: an opening paragraph that sets the scene, a Quick Take summary box above, and then a detailed breakdown of the food, space, and value. This paragraph is here to show the body text styling at its intended reading width.</p>

      <h2>Section Heading Placeholder</h2>

      <p>Section body text goes here. This demonstrates the heading and body text relationship within the article content area. The serif font provides a comfortable reading experience for longer editorial content. Paragraphs are spaced generously to give the eye room to breathe.</p>

      <figure class="inline-photo">
        <div class="image-placeholder">[ Inline Photo Placeholder ]</div>
        <figcaption>Photo caption placeholder text. This describes what the reader would see in the actual image.</figcaption>
      </figure>

      <h2>Another Section Heading</h2>

      <p>More body text to demonstrate the article flow. A real review would discuss specific dishes, prices, and the dining experience here. The layout is designed to hold approximately 1,200 to 1,800 words of editorial content comfortably.</p>

      <p>Inline mentions of <strong class="dish-name">Dish Name</strong> <span class="dish-price">(S$XX)</span> appear like this, with the dish name in bold and the price in a lighter weight. This pattern repeats throughout the food breakdown sections of each review.</p>

      <figure class="inline-photo">
        <div class="image-placeholder">[ Inline Photo Placeholder ]</div>
        <figcaption>Another photo caption placeholder describing the image content.</figcaption>
      </figure>

      <h2>Third Section Heading</h2>

      <p>This section continues the review. The sidebar to the right (visible on desktop) contains ad placements that stay sticky as the reader scrolls. On mobile, these move inline between content sections.</p>

      <p>The content width is capped at 680px to maintain an optimal reading line length. Combined with the sidebar, the total layout width reaches approximately 1100px on desktop.</p>

      <!-- Info Block -->
      <aside class="info-block" aria-label="Restaurant information">
        <div class="info-block-title">Restaurant Info</div>
        <dl>
          <dt>Address</dt>
          <dd>123 Street Name, #01-01, Singapore 000000</dd>

          <dt>MRT</dt>
          <dd>Station Name (XX0), 5-min walk</dd>

          <dt>Hours</dt>
          <dd>Mon&ndash;Sun 11am&ndash;10pm</dd>

          <dt>Price Range</dt>
          <dd>S$XX&ndash;$XX per person</dd>

          <dt>Reservation</dt>
          <dd>Walk-in only</dd>

          <dt>Halal</dt>
          <dd>No</dd>
        </dl>
      </aside>

      <!-- Verdict -->
      <section class="verdict" aria-label="Verdict">
        <h2>Verdict</h2>
        <div class="verdict-rating">X.X <span>/ 10</span></div>
        <p class="verdict-summary">Verdict summary placeholder text. This is where the reviewer wraps up the overall assessment of the restaurant, noting the highlights and the things that could be improved. The verdict is concise and directly useful to someone deciding whether to visit.</p>
      </section>

    </article>

    <!-- AD SIDEBAR (desktop only) -->
    <aside class="ad-sidebar" aria-label="Advertisements">
      <div class="ad-sidebar-inner">
        <div class="ad-slot">
          <span class="ad-slot-label">Partner</span>
          Advertisement
        </div>
        <div class="ad-slot">
          <span class="ad-slot-label">Partner</span>
          Advertisement
        </div>
      </div>
    </aside>

  </div>

  <!-- ===== MORE FROM EAT ===== -->
  <section class="more-from" aria-label="Related articles">
    <div class="more-from-header">
      <h2 class="more-from-title">More from Eat</h2>
      <a href="/thehansang/eat/" class="more-from-link">View all</div>
    </div>
    <div class="more-from-grid">
      <div class="related-card">
        <div class="related-card-image">[ Image ]</div>
        <div class="related-card-pillar">Eat &middot; Guide</div>
        <div class="related-card-title">Related Article Title Placeholder</div>
        <div class="related-card-excerpt">Description placeholder text goes here.</div>
        <div class="related-card-meta">Coming Soon</div>
      </a>
      <div class="related-card">
        <div class="related-card-image">[ Image ]</div>
        <div class="related-card-pillar">Eat &middot; Versus</div>
        <div class="related-card-title">Related Article Title Placeholder</div>
        <div class="related-card-excerpt">Description placeholder text goes here.</div>
        <div class="related-card-meta">Coming Soon</div>
      </a>
      <div class="related-card">
        <div class="related-card-image">[ Image ]</div>
        <div class="related-card-pillar">Eat &middot; Review</div>
        <div class="related-card-title">Related Article Title Placeholder</div>
        <div class="related-card-excerpt">Description placeholder text goes here.</div>
        <div class="related-card-meta">Coming Soon</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .launch-banner { background: var(--ink); color: var(--cream); text-align: center; padding: 10px 24px; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; }

  /* ===== ARTICLE HEADER ===== */
  .article-header {
    max-width: 780px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 48px 48px 32px;
    text-align: center;
    animation: fadeUp 0.6s ease-out 0.1s both;
  }

  .article-pillar-tag {
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gray-500);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .article-pillar-tag a {
    color: var(--gray-500);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  .article-pillar-tag a:hover { color: var(--ember); }

  .article-header h1 {
    font-family: 'Source Serif 4', serif;
    font-size: 40px;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.18;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    text-wrap: balance;
  }

  .article-byline {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--gray-400);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }
  .separator { margin: 0 8px; color: var(--stone); }
  .author { color: var(--ink); font-weight: 500; }

  /* ===== FEATURED IMAGE ===== */
  .article-featured-image {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 48px 32px;
    animation: fadeUp 0.6s ease-out 0.15s both;
  }

  .image-placeholder {
    width: 100%;
    height: 480px;
    background: var(--stone);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: var(--gray-400);
    font-size: 14px;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .article-featured-image figcaption {
    font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--gray-400);
    margin-top: 12px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  /* ===== VIDEO EMBED ===== */
  .article-video {
    max-width: 480px;
    margin: 0 auto 32px;
    padding: 0 48px;
    animation: fadeUp 0.6s ease-out 0.2s both;
  }

  .article-video-inner {
    position: relative;
    aspect-ratio: 9 / 16;
    max-height: 500px;
    background: var(--stone);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .article-video-placeholder {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    color: var(--gray-400);
    font-size: 13px;
  }

  .article-video-play {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  .article-video-play::after {
    content: '';
    display: block;
    width: 0;
    height: 0;
    border-style: solid;
    border-width: 8px 0 8px 14px;
    border-color: transparent transparent transparent white;
    margin-left: 3px;
  }

  .article-video-caption {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--gray-400);
    margin-top: 12px;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  /* ===== ARTICLE LAYOUT ===== */
  .article-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 300px;
    gap: 48px;
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 48px 64px;
    animation: fadeUp 0.6s ease-out 0.3s both;
  }

  /* ===== MAIN CONTENT ===== */
  .article-content { max-width: 680px; }
  .article-content p {
    font-family: 'Source Serif 4', serif;
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .article-content h2 {
    font-family: 'Source Serif 4', serif;
    font-size: 26px;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.3;
    margin-top: 48px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  /* Quick Take */
  .quick-take { border: 1.5px solid var(--stone); padding: 28px 32px; margin-bottom: 40px; background: var(--white); }
  .quick-take-title { font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gray-400); margin-bottom: 20px; padding-bottom: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--stone); }
  .quick-take-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 16px 32px; }
  .quick-take-item { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 4px; }
  .quick-take-label { font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gray-400); }
  .quick-take-value { font-family: 'Source Serif 4', serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--ink); }
  .quick-take-value.rating { color: var(--ember); font-size: 18px; }

  /* Inline photo */
  .inline-photo { margin: 36px 0; }
  .inline-photo .image-placeholder { width: 100%; height: 360px; }
  .inline-photo figcaption { font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: var(--gray-400); margin-top: 10px; line-height: 1.5; }

  /* Dish highlights */
  .dish-name { font-weight: 700; }
  .dish-price { font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; color: var(--gray-500); font-weight: 400; }

  /* Info block */
  .info-block { border: 1.5px solid var(--stone); padding: 28px 32px; margin-top: 48px; margin-bottom: 48px; background: var(--white); }
  .info-block-title { font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gray-400); margin-bottom: 20px; padding-bottom: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--stone); }
  .info-block dl { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 120px 1fr; gap: 12px 16px; }
  .info-block dt { font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gray-400); padding-top: 2px; }
  .info-block dd { font-family: 'Source Serif 4', serif; font-size: 15px; color: var(--ink); line-height: 1.6; }

  /* Verdict */
  .verdict { margin-top: 48px; padding-top: 32px; border-top: 1.5px solid var(--stone); }
  .verdict h2 { margin-top: 0; }
  .verdict-rating { font-family: 'Source Serif 4', serif; font-size: 48px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--ember); line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .verdict-rating span { font-size: 24px; color: var(--gray-400); font-weight: 400; }
  .verdict-summary { font-family: 'Source Serif 4', serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--gray-500); margin-top: 16px; }

  /* ===== AD SIDEBAR ===== */
  .ad-sidebar { position: relative; }
  .ad-sidebar-inner { position: sticky; top: 90px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 32px; }
  .ad-slot { width: 300px; height: 250px; border: 2px dashed var(--stone); display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: var(--gray-400); font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; background: var(--white); }
  .ad-slot-label { font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gray-400); border: 1px solid var(--stone); padding: 1px 6px; margin-bottom: 8px; }

  /* ===== MORE FROM EAT ===== */
  .more-from { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 48px 64px; border-top: 1px solid var(--stone); animation: fadeUp 0.6s ease-out 0.4s both; }
  .more-from-header { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: baseline; padding: 32px 0 24px; }
  .more-from-title { font-family: 'Source Serif 4', serif; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--ink); }
  .more-from-link { font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gray-500); text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.2s; }
  .more-from-link:hover { color: var(--ink); }
  .more-from-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 0; }
  .related-card { padding: 0 24px; border-right: 1px solid var(--stone); text-decoration: none; color: var(--ink); transition: opacity 0.2s; }
  .related-card:first-child { padding-left: 0; }
  .related-card:last-child { padding-right: 0; border-right: none; }
  .related-card:hover { opacity: 0.75; }
  .related-card-image { width: 100%; height: 180px; background: var(--stone); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 11px; color: var(--gray-400); margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .related-card-pillar { font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gray-500); margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .related-card-title { font-family: 'Source Serif 4', serif; font-size: 17px; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.35; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .related-card-excerpt { font-size: 14px; color: var(--gray-500); line-height: 1.55; }
  .related-card-meta { font-size: 11px; color: var(--gray-400); letter-spacing: 0.06em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-top: 10px; }

  /* ===== RESPONSIVE ===== */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .article-header { padding: 32px 24px 24px; }
    .article-header h1 { font-size: 28px; }
    .article-featured-image { padding: 0 24px 24px; }
    .image-placeholder { height: 280px; }
    .article-video { padding: 0 24px; }
    .article-layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; padding: 0 24px 48px; }
    .ad-sidebar { display: none; }
    .quick-take { padding: 20px 24px; }
    .quick-take-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .info-block { padding: 20px 24px; }
    .info-block dl { grid-template-columns: 100px 1fr; }
    .more-from { padding: 0 24px 48px; }
    .more-from-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 24px; }
    .related-card { padding: 0; border-right: none; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--stone); padding-bottom: 24px; }
    .related-card:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .article-header h1 { font-size: 24px; }
    .verdict-rating { font-size: 36px; }
  }
</style>
